# YouTube Ambience Bot - Cron Schedule
#
# To install, run: crontab -e
# Then paste the desired schedule below.
#
# Make sure to update the path to match your installation directory.

# ============================================
# OPTION 1: Daily upload at 10:00 AM (random concept)
# ============================================
# 0 10 * * * /home/omer/projects/youtube-ambience-bot/run.sh >> /home/omer/projects/youtube-ambience-bot/logs/cron.log 2>&1

# ============================================
# OPTION 2: Every 12 hours (random concept)
# ============================================
# 0 */12 * * * /home/omer/projects/youtube-ambience-bot/run.sh >> /home/omer/projects/youtube-ambience-bot/logs/cron.log 2>&1

# ============================================
# OPTION 3: Specific concepts on specific days
# ============================================
# Monday - Cozy fireplace
# 0 10 * * 1 /home/omer/projects/youtube-ambience-bot/run.sh "cozy fireplace" >> /home/omer/projects/youtube-ambience-bot/logs/cron.log 2>&1

# Wednesday - Ocean waves
# 0 10 * * 3 /home/omer/projects/youtube-ambience-bot/run.sh "ocean waves" >> /home/omer/projects/youtube-ambience-bot/logs/cron.log 2>&1

# Friday - Thunderstorm
# 0 10 * * 5 /home/omer/projects/youtube-ambience-bot/run.sh "thunderstorm" >> /home/omer/projects/youtube-ambience-bot/logs/cron.log 2>&1

# ============================================
# QUICK SETUP
# ============================================
# 1. Make run.sh executable: chmod +x run.sh
# 2. Test manually first: ./run.sh
# 3. Edit crontab: crontab -e
# 4. Paste your desired schedule
# 5. Check cron logs: tail -f logs/cron.log
